data.description: If you qualify for a VA loan ask about assuming this loan at a LOW INTEREST RATE. Outstanding home with quality upgrades throughout. Beautiful Open design living area with spacious Great Room, Dining Area & Kitchen and a front Den/Office. Luxury vinyl plank flooring & 9' ceilings on the main level & plush carpet on the upper level. The well appointed Kitchen features 42'' cabinets, high end ss appliances, granite counters & island with breakfast bar & large pantry. Primary Suite walk-in closet & private Bath double sinks & shower. 3 additional BRs, Full Bath & Laundry Rm with attached Flex Room. Full Basement has rough-in for Bath. Additional features include: 2-Car Garage with finished interior & storage space with Level yard backs to tree line. (see A2A notes).
